name: Create Zoho Books vendors from a Google Sheets spreadsheet
description: Import your list of vendors from a Google Sheets spreadsheet and Make will automatically create a vendor contact in Zoho Books for each row. The template uses this [example spreadsheet](https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1GP9tpQ-R8yKY0BM3Pgs-svt4C7vW0j0LcnqT-ZwumQ0/edit?ts=5e4f0895#gid=0).
